<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_d221931bbef8.aspx"><b>晚出新亭</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%8d%97%e5%8c%97%e6%9c%9d">南北朝</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e9%98%b4%e9%93%bf">阴铿</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsond221931bbef8">
<p>大江一浩荡，离悲足几重。<br />潮落犹如盖，云昏不作峰。<br />远戍唯闻鼓，寒山但见松。<br />九十方称半，归途讵有踪。</p>
</div>
</div>
