<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_a929ae77e836.aspx"><b>丰乐亭游春·其三</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e6%ac%a7%e9%98%b3%e4%bf%ae">欧阳修</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsona929ae77e836">
红树青山日欲斜，长郊草色绿无涯。<br />游人不管春将老，来往亭前踏落花。
</div>
