<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_d7d3315f74d4.aspx"><b>于长安归还扬州九月九日行薇山亭赋韵 / 长安九日诗</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%8d%97%e5%8c%97%e6%9c%9d">南北朝</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e6%b1%9f%e6%80%bb">江总</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsond7d3315f74d4">
<p>心逐南云逝，形随北雁来。<br />故乡篱下菊，今日几花开。</p>
